&lt;h3 id=&quot;game-play-ideas&quot;&gt;Game play ideas&lt;&#x2F;h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Maybe the players are hunting these ancient high tech relics? Maybe the stargates will take the players to a high-tech world.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
</content>
        
